  Scenario: --xmpfilter-style
    Given the file "magic_comments.rb":
    """
    1+1# =>
    2+2    # => 10
    "a
     b" # =>
    /a
     b/ # =>
    1
    "omg"
    # =>
    "omg2"
    # => "not omg2"
    """
    When I run "seeing_is_believing --xmpfilter-style magic_comments.rb"
    Then stderr is empty
    And the exit status is 0
    And stdout is:
    """
    1+1# => 2
    2+2    # => 4
    "a
     b" # => "a\n b"
    /a
     b/ # => /a\n b/
    1
    "omg"
    # => "omg"
    "omg2"
    # => "omg2"
    """


